\begin_inset Formula $\psi(e_{i})\approx\psi(e_{i}^{l})-{\displaystyle \sum_{j=1}^{m}\psi'(e_{i}^{l})x_{ij}\Delta\beta_{j}^{(l)}},i=1,2,3,\cdots,n$
\end_inset

